_sText:
After my early release of gg_divine I got a few comments that the map was to simple and didn't provide enough props to the map.  I took these comments and retried my initial intent but this time with success.  I am now happy to say this new version of gg_divine is up for download.

As always I appreciate all feedback I get on my maps.

 
More screenshots are available at http://2021productions.com/?page_id=192

Fill free to check out my portfolio at http://2021productions.com/?page_id=138
